{
  "id": "62811de7d71872002221c1de",
  "title": "平家物語のあらすじ",
  "created": 1652628970,
  "updated": 1652668292,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62811de7d71872002221c1de",
      "text": "平家物語のあらすじ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652628970,
      "updated": 1652628974
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6735e90c00000ba1d68",
      "text": "ざっくり",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668018,
      "updated": 1652668285
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6735e90c00000ba1d69",
      "text": "[https://www.mottainaihonpo.com/kaitori/contents/cat01/045-heikemonogatari.html 【平家物語】328文字であらすじを紹介 滅びと鎮魂の物語]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668018,
      "updated": 1652668027
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b67c5e90c00000ba1d6c",
      "text": ">①[平清盛]が[保元の乱]・[平治の乱]で勝利し、[武士]として初めて[太政大臣]（総理大臣）となる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668027,
      "updated": 1652668076
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6745e90c00000ba1d6b",
      "text": ">②清盛が娘を天皇に嫁がせ、一族の人間を次々に要職へ就かせ、更に膨大な権力を得る",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668019,
      "updated": 1652668047
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6915e90c00000ba1d6d",
      "text": ">③[後白河法皇]を筆頭とする勢力が「[鹿ヶ谷の陰謀]」で打倒平氏を目論むも失敗",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668048,
      "updated": 1652668085
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6975e90c00000ba1d6e",
      "text": ">④後白河法皇の息子・[以仁王]（もちひとおう）が平家追討を諸国に命令、これを機に[源頼朝]などの反平氏勢力が各地で挙兵",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668054,
      "updated": 1652668065
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6735e90c00000ba1d6a",
      "text": ">⑤「[富士川の戦い]」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668018,
      "updated": 1652668120
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6be5e90c00000ba1d72",
      "text": "> 〇 源頼朝 VS [平維盛] ×",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668093,
      "updated": 1652668111
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6b75e90c00000ba1d6f",
      "text": ">⑥清盛が病死",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668086,
      "updated": 1652668100
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6c65e90c00000ba1d73",
      "text": ">⑦「[俱利伽羅峠の戦い]」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668100,
      "updated": 1652668118
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6cb5e90c00000ba1d74",
      "text": "> 〇 [木曽義仲] VS 平維盛 ×",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668106,
      "updated": 1652668115
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6b75e90c00000ba1d70",
      "text": ">⑧頼朝が[源義経]に木曽義仲討伐を命令",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668086,
      "updated": 1652668132
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6e25e90c00000ba1d75",
      "text": "> 「[宇治川の戦い]」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668129,
      "updated": 1652668135
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6e25e90c00000ba1d76",
      "text": "> 〇 源義経 VS 木曽義仲 ×",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668129,
      "updated": 1652668129
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6b85e90c00000ba1d71",
      "text": ">⑨義経が、「[一ノ谷の戦い]」「[屋島の戦い]」と順調に勝ち進む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668086,
      "updated": 1652668150
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6f15e90c00000ba1d78",
      "text": ">⑩義経の活躍により、「[壇ノ浦の戦い]」でついに[平知盛]・[安徳天皇]など平家の要が死亡",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668144,
      "updated": 1652668164
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b6ea5e90c00000ba1d77",
      "text": ">⑪頼朝が義経の討伐命令を出す「[判官都落]」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668136,
      "updated": 1652668176
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b70f5e90c00000ba1d79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668174,
      "updated": 1652668174
    },
    {
      "id": "6281b7835e90c00000ba1d90",
      "text": "もっと詳しく",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652668289,
      "updated": 1652668292
    },
